---
layout: base.njk
title: "Age Calculator"
---

<main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="space-y-4">
<div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary/10 border border-tertiary/20 text-tertiary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]" data-icon="auto_awesome">auto_awesome</span>
<span>Vitality Analytics</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Age Calculator.</h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                    Map your trajectory through time with celestial precision. Understand your duration, celebrate your milestones, and prepare for the next orbit.
                </p>
</header>
<!-- Tool Interface (Asymmetrical Bento Grid) -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
<!-- Input Card -->
<section class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
<div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-8">
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-on-surface-variant ml-1">Date of Birth</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-highest border-none rounded-2xl py-4 px-6 text-on-surface focus:ring-0 focus:border-b focus:border-primary transition-all" type="date" value="1995-06-15"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-on-surface-variant ml-1">Target Date</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-highest border-none rounded-2xl py-4 px-6 text-on-surface focus:ring-0 focus:border-b focus:border-primary transition-all" type="date" value="2024-05-20"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<button class="w-full hero-gradient py-4 rounded-2xl text-on-primary-container font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(185,195,255,0.3)] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
<span>Calculate Chronology</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="hourglass_empty">hourglass_empty</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Informational Slice -->
<div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-3xl flex items-center space-x-4 border-l-4 border-tertiary">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tertiary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary" data-icon="lightbulb">lightbulb</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-on-surface font-bold">Time Fact</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">An average human heart beats about 2.5 billion times in a lifetime.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Result Card -->
<section class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
<div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden">
<!-- Decorative radial glow -->
<div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 space-y-10">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start">
<h3 class="text-on-surface-variant font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Temporal Status</h3>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="timeline">timeline</span>
</div>
<!-- Age Main Display -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
<div class="text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter">28</div>
<div class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">Years</div>
</div>
<div class="text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter">11</div>
<div class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">Months</div>
</div>
<div class="text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter">05</div>
<div class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">Days</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Secondary Stats Grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl flex justify-between items-center bg-white/5">
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Total Months</p>
<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface">347</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary" data-icon="calendar_view_month">calendar_view_month</span>
</div>
<div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl flex justify-between items-center bg-white/5">
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Total Days</p>
<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface">10,568</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary" data-icon="event_note">event_note</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Next Birthday Section -->
<div class="bg-indigo-900/20 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-indigo-500/20">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
<div class="space-y-1">
<h4 class="text-indigo-200 font-bold text-lg">Next Birthday Countdown</h4>
<p class="text-indigo-300/60 text-sm">Approaching your next solar return</p>
</div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-300" data-icon="cake">cake</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-end space-x-2">
<span class="text-5xl font-black text-indigo-300 tracking-tighter leading-none">26</span>
<span class="text-indigo-400 font-bold mb-1">Days Remaining</span>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 w-full h-2 bg-indigo-950 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-indigo-400 w-[92%] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(129,140,248,0.5)]"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
<!-- Visual Editorial Break -->
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
<div class="relative h-64 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden group">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="conceptual photo of a vintage pocket watch floating in a dark ethereal void with particles of light" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBk9gowKna3pb_jcME-YqDBOzi7o-DhGwM3i0ok8W6V1rgb6xZfB6nmylxZU4VgFMh0lh1vsQJFmOppKfni-DMYYPCSqwm8Z42aU_K_nyiyxzAzmf0orquEIuWivL4AF5H7K9NiDuVsCvSBTA7Dkm5YAQi6kmYmaLtcJMIiqG5fUsuBI0YTvuCt4eLtKcedHhBd-lJFDuoTdE0eVkyi5aXgeIXgQRZCFfCVN7HW7r1NvpKWsbAqP4f8CLF46J1Y1EQ1cluH2Vx6M6s"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent p-6 flex flex-col justify-end">
<p class="text-white font-bold">Chronos</p>
<p class="text-white/60 text-xs">The linear progression</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-2 glass-panel p-8 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-center">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Your journey by the numbers.</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                        Beyond years and months, life is lived in the micro-moments. Since your birth, you have shared approximately 840 million seconds of breath with the world. This tool helps you visualize that vast expanse of time through a modern, crystalline interface designed for clarity.
                    </p>
</div>
</section>
</div>

</main>